ed on the periodic\ntrajectories computed in the previous iteration for its upstream links. The\nresulting iterates are shown to converge uniformly monotonically to the desired\nperiodic orbit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 May 2017 19:21:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Sep 2017 19:09:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-13"}
