d in previous studies have only a minor influence on\nion and photon yields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 May 2017 23:54:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2022 17:55:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
