trast, our results\nsuggest that today's mid-sized moons are likely re-accreted from such a\ncatastrophic event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 May 2017 04:57:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 02:07:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-04"}
