 of the\ngroup ${\\bf F}_q^*$. This implies that $(u_j(D), c_{k-1}(u_j(x)))$ is a deep\nhole of ${\\rm GPRS}_q(D, k)$ if $p|k$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 May 2017 15:59:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-23"}
